        <title>Fake-Claiming on Trial</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Reaper]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Any kind of prestige given to “always tell the truth as BD on stand” will heavily influence people to continue metas where they up only for claims. In my opinion, this is a lazy and uninteractive gameplan (not that different from WKM). If the game design follow this same lead, the meta will always be like this, hence some of the reasons why I dropped the game. I mean, why there was a change to not being able to edit logs at stand again?</p>
          <p><a href="https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/fake-claiming-on-trial/77486/130">Read full topic</a></p>
